美国两名议员宣布自我隔离。
Two U. S. lawmakers have declared self-imposed isolation.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 南博一3月8日，两名美国共和党议员相继宣布将自我隔离14天，此前他们都出席了在马里兰州举行的保守派政治行动（CPAC）会议。
NEW YORK (Reuters) - Two U.S. Republican lawmakers announced they would isolate themselves for 14 days after attending a meeting of the Conservative Political Action (CPAC) in Maryland.
3月7日，美国保守派联盟（ACU）宣布，在前一周举行的保守派政治行动会议上，一名与会者确诊感染了新冠肺炎。
On March 7, the American Conservative Union (ACU) announced that a participant at a Conservative Political Action meeting the previous week had confirmed that he had contracted pneumonia.
特德·克鲁兹据美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）3月8日报道，得克萨斯州参议员、共和党人特德·克鲁兹和亚利桑那州众议员、共和党人保罗·戈萨尔分别表示，他们将进行为期14天的自我隔离，并谨慎行事。
Texas Senator Ted Cruz and Republican Representative Paul Gossar of Arizona said they would isolate themselves for 14 days and proceed cautiously, according to CNN.
目前两人还没有出现新冠病毒感染的任何症状。
The two men have yet to show any signs of a new crown virus infection.
特德·克鲁兹表示，他将在14日内一直待在得克萨斯州。
Ted Cruz said he would be in Texas for 14 days.
他表示自己曾与确诊者进行“简单的谈话并握手”，但持续的时间不足一分钟，卫生机构认为他感染的可能性很低。
He said he had a "simple conversation and handshake" with the patient, but for less than a minute, the health authorities said he had a low risk of infection.
保罗·戈萨尔则在8日晚些时候发表的声明中表示，他与确诊者待在一起的时间很长，“握了好几次手”。
Paul Gossar said in a statement later in the day that he had spent a long time with the patients, "shaking hands several times."
他宣布将在自己位于亚利桑那州的家中待14天，他的办公室将关闭一周。
He announced that he would spend 14 days at his home in Arizona and that his office would be closed for a week.
2月26日至29日，保守派政治行动会议在美国马里兰州举行。
The Conservative Political Action Conference was held in Maryland, United States, from 26 to 29 February.
美国总统特朗普、副总统彭斯及多名高官均出席了此次会议。
US President Trump, Vice President Burns, and a number of senior officials attended the meeting.
3月7日，美国保守派联盟发表声明称，一名参会人员确诊感染新冠肺炎，但该与会人员并没有与特朗普或彭斯接触，也没有参加当天在主会场举行的活动。
On March 7, the American Conservative Union issued a statement saying that one of the attendees had been diagnosed with New Crown Pneumonia, but the attendees had no contact with Trump or Burns and did not attend an event on the main floor that day.
特朗普在得知这一消息后也表示，他对此并不担心。
When Trump heard the news, he said he was not worried about it.
